Definition: a deceptive way of selling that involves advertising a product at a very low price in order to attract customers who are then persuaded to switch to a more expensive product
Synonyms: selling, a, deceptive, way, of, that, involves, advertising, product, at, very, low, price, in, order, to, attract, customers, who, are, then, persuaded, switch, more, expensive
Category: noun.act
